<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV27">
<l>viṇkaṭanta cōtiyāy viḷaṅkuñāṉa mūrttiyāyp</l>
<l>paṇkaṭanta tēcamēvu pāvanāca nātaṉē</l>
<l>eṇkaṭanta yōkiṉōṭi rantuceṉṟu māṇiyāy</l>
<l>maṇkaṭanta vaṇṇaniṉṉai yārmatikka vallarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Flame that transcends the sky! O You whose form is shining knowledge!</l>
<l>O sin-removing Lord who abides in the land that is beyond [the reach of]</l>
<l rend="indent">the Sound (=Vedas)!</l>
<l>Who can assess You [and] the way [You] measured the earth as a Dwarf,</l>
<l>having gone begging [for it], with a countless [number] of tricks!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
